374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Volunteer</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-dem-gray-600\">Help with voter registration, phone banking, canvassing, and events.</p><a class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\" href=\"/contact\">Sign Up<!-- --> →</a></div><div class=\"group rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex rounded-lg bg-dem-blue/10 p-3 text-dem-blue\"><svg class=\"h-8 w-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Attend Meetings</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-dem-gray-600\">Join our monthly Central Committee meetings at the Ukiah Valley Conference Center.</p><a class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\" href=\"/events\">View Events<!-- --> →</a></div><div class=\"group rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex rounded-lg bg-dem-blue/10 p-3 text-dem-blue\"><svg class=\"h-8 w-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Join a Club</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-dem-gray-600\">Connect with Democrats in your area through one of our chartered clubs.</p><a class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\" href=\"/clubs\">Find a Club<!-- --> →</a></div><div class=\"group rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex rounded-lg bg-dem-blue/10 p-3 text-dem-blue\"><svg class=\"h-8 w-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Donate</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-dem-gray-600\">Support our efforts to register voters and elect Democrats in Mendocino County.</p><a class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\" href=\"/donate\">Donate Now<!-- --> →</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative h-64 sm:h-80\"><img alt=\"Mendocino County redwood forests\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dem-gray-50 to-transparent\"></div></section><section class=\"bg-dem-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"prose max-w-none\"><p>Democracy works best when everyone participates. There are many ways you can get involved with the Mendocino County Democratic Party and make a difference in your community.</p>\n<h2>Volunteer</h2>\n<p>We always need enthusiastic volunteers to help with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Voter Registration Drives</strong> — Help fellow citizens register to vote</li>\n<li><strong>Phone Banking &#x26; Canvassing</strong> — Reach out to voters during election season</li>\n<li><strong>Event Planning</strong> — Help organize our meetings, fundraisers, and community events</li>\n<li><strong>Social Media</strong> — Help spread the word about our candidates and issues online</li>\n<li><strong>Office Support</strong> — Administrative tasks that keep our operation running smoothly</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Attend Our Meetings</h2>\n<p>Our Central Committee holds monthly meetings that are open to all registered Democrats. It's a great way to meet like-minded people, hear from candidates, and stay informed about local political issues.</p>\n<h2>Run for Office</h2>\n<p>Interested in running for local office? We support and mentor Democratic candidates at all levels. Whether you're considering a run for school board, city council, county supervisor, or another position, we're here to help.</p>\n<h2>Join a Democratic Club</h2>\n<p>Mendocino County has several chartered Democratic clubs that meet regularly. Find one near you on our Chartered Clubs page and get connected with Democrats in your area.</p>\n<h2>Register to Vote</h2>\n<p>If you're not already registered, or if you've moved recently, make sure your voter registration is up to date. Visit <a href=\"https://registertovote.ca.gov/\">RegisterToVote.ca.gov</a> to register or update your information.</p>\n<h2>Stay Informed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow us on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mendodems/\">Facebook</a></li>\n<li>Attend our events and meetings</li>\n<li>Check our website regularly for news and updates</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-dem-red py-16\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\"><img alt=\"Voting\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-15\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-vote.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white\">Are You Registered to Vote?</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/90\">Make sure your voter registration is up to date. It only takes a few m